"title": "8322: perfection, human",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8322",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Human wholeness in the image of God, given at creation and lost in the fall, is to be fully restored in Jesus Christ.</p>\n<h2>Humanity was created perfect</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:26-Gen1:27\">GEN 1:26–1:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen5:1\">GEN 5:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek28:12-Ezek28:15\">EZK 28:12–28:15</a> <em>The king of Tyre is described in terms of the creation and fall of humanity</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:9\">JAS 3:9</a></p>\n<h2>Perfection was lost through sin</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:23\">ROM 3:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:17\">GEN 2:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:16-Gen3:19\">GEN 3:16–3:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:23\">GEN 3:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job15:14-Job15:16\">JOB 15:14–15:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek28:15-Ezek28:17\">EZK 28:15–28:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:21\">ROM 1:21</a></p>\n<h2>The need for moral perfection</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut18:13\">DEU 18:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen17:1\">GEN 17:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job25:4\">JOB 25:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps24:3-Ps24:4\">PSA 24:3–24:4</a></p>\n<h2>Human inability to keep God's law perfectly</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb7:19\">HEB 7:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb7:11\">HEB 7:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:1\">HEB 10:1</a></p>\n<h2>Perfection and redemption</h2>\n<h3>God's purpose for believers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:22\">COL 1:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan11:35\">DAN 11:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan12:10\">DAN 12:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:27\">EPH 5:27</a> <em>God's purpose for the church</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:14\">HEB 10:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:40\">HEB 11:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:23\">HEB 12:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:4\">JAS 1:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:24\">JUD 1:24</a></p>\n<h3>The aim of Christian ministry</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:28\">COL 1:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:2\">2CO 11:2</a></p>\n<h3>The aim of the Christian</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:12\">PHP 3:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor13:9-2Cor13:11\">2CO 13:9–13:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:13\">EPH 4:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:1\">HEB 6:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:4\">JAS 1:4</a></p>\n<h2>Characteristics of perfection</h2>\n<h3>Perfect love</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:48\">MAT 5:48</a></strong> <em>Jesus Christ patterning his disciples' love on the love God has for all people.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:12\">1JN 4:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:18\">1JN 4:18</a></p>\n<h3>Perfect holiness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor7:1\">2CO 7:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:10\">PHP 1:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:15\">PHP 2:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:27\">JAS 1:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:14\">2PE 3:14</a></p>\n<h3>Perfect obedience</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:14\">1TI 6:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:5\">1JN 2:5</a></p>\n<h3>Perfect speech</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:2\">JAS 3:2</a></p>\n<h3>Perfect unity with other believers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:23\">JHN 17:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:10\">1CO 1:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:14\">COL 3:14</a></p>\n<h3>Perfect joy</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:11\">JHN 15:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:29\">JHN 3:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:24\">JHN 16:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:4\">1JN 1:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2John1:12\">2JN 1:12</a></p>\n<h3>Perfect peace</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:3\">ISA 26:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:165\">PSA 119:165</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:7\">PHP 4:7</a></p>\n<h3>Perfect knowledge</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor13:9-1Cor13:12\">1CO 13:9–13:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:14\">ROM 15:14</a> <em>Although complete knowledge is inaccessible here and now, believers have all they need to live the Christian life</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:2\">COL 2:2</a></p>\n<h2>Perfection in describing human physical beauty</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam14:25-2Sam14:27\">2SA 14:25–14:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song4:7\">SNG 4:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song5:2\">SNG 5:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song6:9\">SNG 6:9</a></p>\n<h2>False claims to perfection</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job36:4\">JOB 36:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps64:6\">PSA 64:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:96\">PSA 119:96</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek27:3-Ezek27:4\">EZK 27:3–27:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:6\">PHP 3:6</a></p>",
